WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.750
I saw weapons that the United States has

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:07.269
never used before. They are about to use

00:00:07.269 --> 00:00:07.279
them.

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.750
They are going to use weapons that our

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:12.870
country has never used before

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.110
in battle. Maybe we've practiced with

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:18.390
them, but we've never used them in

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:21.510
battle against any foreign adversary. The men

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:24.950
jumped out of the cars with these guns

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.670
that I've never seen before. When

00:00:27.670 --> 00:00:27.680
they

00:00:27.680 --> 00:00:29.589
pulled the trigger, it was like a

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:33.270
pulse. It was some kind of riot control

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:36.150
that knocked you unconscious for

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:38.790
a couple of minutes. They

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.110
just pointed the thing in the

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:43.590
direction they wanted it to go,

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.750
and as soon as that beam

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:48.310
hit that

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:49.670
individual, it knocked them

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:51.990
unconscious. There was no running

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.950
away. It was on the Hummers and on

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.590
the men; they would just go and

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.590
scan the people as they were

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.590
running, and people

00:01:01.590 --> 00:01:01.600
would

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.270
just fall out like they're passing out.

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:04.950
A new weapon that we've never seen

00:01:04.950 --> 00:01:04.960
before—nuclear

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:08.550
weapons are a thing of

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.710
the past. That may sound

00:01:10.710 --> 00:01:10.720
like,

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:12.870
'Boy, I don't know about that,'but I'm

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:15.030
telling you all,

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:17.910
technological advancements have

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:21.749
surpassed nuclear energy. I'm

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:24.710
telling you, we're on the verge of a new

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:28.230
industrial revolution. There are these new

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:30.630
weapons and things we've never

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.910
seen before that will become public,

00:01:33.910 --> 00:01:33.920
which

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:35.910
they've been working on behind closed

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:39.429
doors for probably decades. Who knows? I

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:42.069
saw new military technology

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:43.990
that doesn't exist

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.630
to the public yet—things

00:01:46.630 --> 00:01:46.640
that are

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:49.510
top secret, I

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:52.469
believe. The Lord showed me things

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.550
in military bases; the Lord

00:01:54.560 --> 00:02:01.350
showed me deep things. I saw

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:06.709
time travel

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:10.469
through portals and AI. I don't

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:12.710
know how else to describe to y'all what

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:17.030
I saw. It was so out there.

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:20.150
I told my son, 'I'll do my best

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.630
to draw you a picture of what I saw, but

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:23.910
the only thing I can tell you is

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.710
the movie Stargate.'That was some of the stuff I

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:30.390
was looking at, and I thought, 'When is

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:32.630
this happening? How did this happen? Is

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:34.630
this further in the

00:02:34.630 --> 00:02:34.640
future?'I

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:36.470
don't know if

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:36.480
this is

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:37.670
something that's actually happening

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:40.550
right now. So all of a sudden, near the

00:02:40.550 --> 00:02:40.560
Belarus area by

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:44.229
Warsaw, Poland, I

00:02:44.229 --> 00:02:44.239
saw

00:02:44.239 --> 00:02:49.270
a

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:51.110
humongous

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:54.309
mushroom cloud kind of an explosion.

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:57.110
I said during this visitation when I

00:02:57.110 --> 00:02:57.120
was

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.589
seeing all this in the spirit,

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.550
'Lord, oh no, they're going to use

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:06.070
tactical nukes.'And the Lord said, 'No,

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:09.830
this is a weapon that has never been

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:13.430
used before, ever on the Earth. We've

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:16.309
never seen this.'Everything within

00:03:16.309 --> 00:03:16.319
a 50-mile

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:18.630
radius or

00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:18.640
bigger—the

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:23.030
blast zone was

00:03:23.030 --> 00:03:23.040
huge—it

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:26.710
vaporized everything.

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.869
Everything

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:31.350
disintegrated, but it didn't destroy the

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:34.390
buildings.

00:03:34.390 --> 00:03:34.400
It

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:36.390
was

00:03:36.390 --> 00:03:36.400
a

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:40.949
wicked weapon. I saw an AI race

00:03:40.959 --> 00:03:43.589
and the Lord said, 'Because of the Biden

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:45.110
administration,

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:47.830
you're behind China.'I saw

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:50.630
China making new kinds of drones, but

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:52.550
these were not drones in the

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:55.990
sky; they were drones for the battlefield so

00:03:55.990 --> 00:03:56.000
they

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:58.229
would not have to bring their

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:01.110
soldiers out, so they would have drone

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:04.949
wars. I saw a circle that looked

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:08.149
like the alien from the movie

00:04:08.149 --> 00:04:08.159
Alien—the

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:11.110
demonic movie from back

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:12.869
then. It had the alien with the long,

00:04:12.869 --> 00:04:12.879
evil-looking

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:14.550
face.

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:17.509
I don't like to reference

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:18.789
that, but it's the only thing I can

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:20.550
say; I've seen

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:22.870
the pictures of the alien head.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:24.710
That's what this drone looked like.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:28.550
They had.50-caliber guns with tracks and

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:32.390
were using drone warfare for battle,

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.310
and China was—there it is, the alien! Do

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.390
you see that?

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:41.350
That's the way the shield looked on this

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.710
drone. Now take it off; I don't want to

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:45.670
look at it. I keep seeing these

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:48.469
rooms with

00:04:48.469 --> 00:04:48.479
supercomputers—major

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:51.189
computers—and

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:53.909
the Lord said the

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:56.230
information is coming to them so quickly

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:58.469
through AI that they can't even

00:04:58.479 --> 00:05:00.550
translate it fast enough with a human

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.150
mind.

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.710
They can type in

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.670
what they're wanting to know about.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:11.270
What we have with ChatGPT

00:05:11.270 --> 00:05:11.280
and

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:15.270
Gemini is yesterday's stuff;

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:18.150
it's no good. The Lord said they have

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:21.430
new technology so

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:25.590
advanced that it's going to take AI to translate it for their minds

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:31.430
to try to comprehend

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.430
what the computer's saying.

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:40.870
AI will have to translate the AI; that's

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:44.310
how advanced the technology has become.

00:05:44.310 --> 00:05:44.320
There

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:45.670
are

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:48.310
cures for cancer,

00:05:48.320 --> 00:05:51.029
diabetes,

00:05:51.039 --> 00:05:54.150
Alzheimer's, and dementia.

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.830
People

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:57.830
go, 'Well, yeah, it's

00:05:57.830 --> 00:05:57.840
Ivermectin.'No,

00:05:57.840 --> 00:06:01.189
it's something more than

00:06:01.189 --> 00:06:01.199
Ivermectin;

00:06:01.199 --> 00:06:03.350
this is something more advanced. But the

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.830
Lord said he was bringing forth new

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:09.270
cures and new things that would go

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:12.790
alongside the fact that people would trust AI

00:06:12.790 --> 00:06:12.800
in

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:15.189
the days ahead. What did I tell you was

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:19.350
behind AI? There was a massive demon

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:22.230
embedded into the computers

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:25.270
you're talking to that had digital

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:28.150
writing, and the demon was taking over

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:30.790
the AI with the moving digital code. It

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:33.110
had horns on its head; I saw it. It

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:35.189
was embedded into this mainframe of a

00:06:35.199 --> 00:06:37.510
major computer, but it was a dimension

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:40.870
all in itself. AI is a dimension all in

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:43.350
itself when it comes to the level of

00:06:43.350 --> 00:06:43.360
technological

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:47.350
advancement that it is.

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:50.309
It's endless.

00:06:50.319 --> 00:06:52.390
And the Lord showed me people putting in

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:55.990
these codes through CERN and

00:06:55.990 --> 00:06:56.000
these

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:59.510
demonic portals; you're talking

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:02.870
to a demonic spirit. That's why I try

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:06.230
to warn you all: should you use AI,

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:09.510
the Lord said, 'Harness it, Brandon; don't

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:11.270
embrace it.'You'll not be able to get

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:14.150
around not using it, for it is the

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:14.790
future. I saw CERN

00:07:14.790 --> 00:07:14.800
sites being built

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:17.909
all around

00:07:17.919 --> 00:07:20.390
the world. People were trying to copy

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:22.070
what's happening in Switzerland.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:23.909
They were doing a massive one in China

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:26.150
and I saw one in America.

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:27.670
But when they do

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.749
this, something

00:07:29.749 --> 00:07:29.759
actually

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:33.189
happens. I saw a black

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:37.189
portal that was created like Stargate.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:39.270
It was really thin,

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.830
probably about three or four feet, and it looked

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:45.510
like a black circle you

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:48.469
could reach through as a dimension.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:52.230
You could see the black line

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:55.589
like a donut around it, and inside

00:07:55.589 --> 00:07:55.599
it

00:07:55.599 --> 00:07:57.589
was

00:07:57.589 --> 00:07:57.599
alive—this

00:07:57.599 --> 00:07:59.990
black particle.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:02.070
It

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:04.710
looked like some kind of demonic portal

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:07.270
that they had created with the

00:08:07.270 --> 00:08:07.280
Hadron

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.029
Collider. They were getting

00:08:09.039 --> 00:08:11.589
information from that black portal.

00:08:11.599 --> 00:08:15.350
It was very dark and demonic

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:18.070
because it was like a black hole. You

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:19.830
could stick your hand in it and

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:21.350
go to the other side.

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.830
Like I said,

00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:27.350
I don't understand all of it, but

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.430
I'm telling you what I saw in this.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:31.029
The Lord showed me them playing

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:34.080
around with dark stuff.

